snippet.title: No Greater Love
snippet.description:
I work alone in my home creating these films. There is no '"Reader", "Presenter" or "Narrator" as such - only me.

My aim is to disseminate scripture; make people think a little more about scripture, and further a far-deeper understanding of Biblical texts. Primarily, I want to reach existing people of Faith and help them become even greater ambassadors of God. 
I seek to bolster, embolden & edify the existing Faith of people of God. I also seek to start pockets of revival as a result.

In my personal life, I seek anointing of the Holy Spirit that I may anoint others to anoint others. Exponential evangelism.
I pray a LOT.
Much of what I do seems in response to God's Holy Spirit.  All for the Glory of God and the furtherance of His holy kingdom.

SUPPORT: No Greater Love & The Commands of Jesus at:
   https://patreon.com/No_Greater_Love
   https://paypal.me/NoGreaterLoveYouTube

For a free copy of Commands of Jesus PDF, visit:  https://mailchi.mp/d0847ab0f0a0/commands_of_jesus_pdf_free
